00:01:15.660 --> 00:01:17.306
these two characters.

00:01:17.306 --> 00:01:20.097
So in that sense, just about[br]every comic book character

00:01:20.097 --> 00:01:21.787
could be considered a rip-off

00:01:21.787 --> 00:01:23.546
