00:01:31.333 --> 00:01:32.935
And his costume drew inspiration

00:01:32.935 --> 00:01:36.180
from Flash Gordon and aliens[br]from old pulp magazines,

00:01:36.180 --> 00:01:38.456
mixed with a little bit[br]of circus strong man

00:01:38.456 --> 00:01:40.348
thrown in there with the red trunks.

00:01:40.348 --> 00:01:42.821
Batman creators Bill Finger and Bob Kane

00:01:42.821 --> 00:01:46.411
also had a slew of influences,[br]from The Shadow, Zorro,

00:01:46.411 --> 00:01:48.617
